			"relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 года назад",
			"rating": 1,
			"text": {
				"text": "It was AWFUL !!!\nI came late evening before 4 days off with my child that had a broken tooth. The doctor didn't have a look, just told me that she is busy and can not help. I was pleading her to show me on the Google map where should I run to, but she just called the next patient and didn't pay attention to me!\nThan I bagged her at least to give me a name and she quickly wrote a name (that I didn't find on the map) and locked the door I front of my face!\nI DON'T recommend to go to this clinic - thise are not doctors, they are just moneymakers.\nPS: lower Mr. Emran Elezovic is just a liar. The doctor didn't explained me anything. She ignored me. Finally I cryed: help me at least to find smb else, what a doctor you are! And she gave me that paper with a name that is not on the Google map.\nDon't lie, Mr. Emran. It's a sin.",
				"languageCode": "en"
			},
			"originalText": {
